{"tid":1818874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地來港僅數天 3歲童猝死家中 房署派人走廊消毒","createTime":"2020-01-10T09:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T10:22:38.000Z","uid":44562,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"630b3cfb404b3d8e5a1ebb7143805617830c9b76","tid":1818874,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:41:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200110/60468836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200110%2F60468836&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=41c16394\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200110%2F60468836&h=69c59342\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200110/60468836</a><br />\n本港處於流感高峰期之際，有3歲病童咳嗽不適，家人未有即時求醫，至今凌晨猝死家中。九龍灣啟業邨啟賢樓，凌晨約1時半，一名3歲內地男童被母親發現屋內暈倒，昏迷不醒，家人大驚下由男童的舅父報警，男童由救護員送往聯合醫院搶救，可惜約1小時後不治。據悉，由於醫護人員發現男童身上有傷痕，故警方CID正調查案件，其死因有待驗屍後確定，案件暫列送院時死亡。"},{"pid":"2c6db20acf7f0bc72af911e58df688a619cae070","tid":1818874,"uid":314679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:42:06.000Z","msg":"仆街啦"},{"pid":"f2b146a12e108804fe1293cf99abd2d512747ea1","tid":1818874,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"落黎替死咩支那種<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n屌 真係替死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051ac332621dc9af3d7aa2f1e45ba53e0bd2d2b0","tid":181887